          'Freedom to think without algorithmic manipulation',
          'Transparency in AI decision-making processes',
          'User control over AI recommendations',
          'Resistance to cognitive behavioral modification',
          'Preservation of human agency in AI interactions',
        ],
      },
    },
    applications: {
      title: 'Applied Philosophy in Technology',
      description:
        'These principles guide every technical decision, from architecture choices to user interface design. The goal is technology that empowers individuals while resisting state control.',
